<paragraph blockId="3.[784,1380,296,723]" pageId="3" pageNumber="598">on the head and are conspicuous. Tail is long and slender and covered with rings of small scales. Dental formulais 2/1, C 1/1, P 3/3, M 3/3 (x2) = 34.</paragraph>
